## Customization

### Adding Packages

Edit `flake.nix` and add to `extraConfig`:

```nix
extraConfig = {
  environment.systemPackages = with pkgs; [
    # your-package-here
  ];
};
```

### Changing Settings

All NixOS options can be added to `extraConfig` in `flake.nix`.

See [NixOS Options](https://search.nixos.org/options) for available options.

### User-Specific Configuration

Edit `user.nix` to customize:
- Extra groups
- Home-manager settings
- User packages

